ext":"In &quot;Sin \u0627\u0644\u0625\u062b\u0645&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Sin \u0627\u0644\u0625\u062b\u0645","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/sin-al-ithm\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":11275,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2013\/01\/09\/dajjal-people-flee-to-mountains\/","url_meta":{"origin":25039,"position":2},"title":"Hadith on Dajjal: People flee False Messiah to the mountains","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"January 9, 2013","format":false,"excerpt":"Umm Sharik reported: The Prophet, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cThe people will flee from the False Messiah into the mountains.\u201d She said, \u201cO Messenger of Allah, where will the Arabs be on that day?\u201d The Prophet said, \u201cThey will be few.\u201d Source: S\u0323ah\u0323i\u0304h\u0323\u00a0Muslim 2945 Grade: Sahih (authentic)\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/wisdom-al-hikmah\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":32543,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2019\/06\/28\/seek-refuge-vices-fitnah\/","url_meta":{"origin":25039,"position":3},"title":"Hadith on Dua: Seek refuge from vices, trials, and oppression","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"June 28, 2019","format":false,"excerpt":"Anas ibn Malik reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, would say, \u201cO Allah, I seek refuge in You from disability, sloth, cowardice, senility, and miserliness. I seek refuge in You from the torment of the grave and from the trials of life and death.\u201d Source:\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u06